title: 3-Channel Cord Protector & Cable Cover to Prevent Tripping Accident for Floor by UT Wire
description:
UT Wire - 3-Channel Cord Protector & Concealer

Having more cords than you think that needs to run across the floor? Not only it is a major safety issue in home and office waiting to happen, it is also unsightly. A great home office organization idea is to apply cable protector to keep the cables down from potential tripping hazard. This 3-channel Cord Protector and Concealer can easily install to take care this issue. Specially designed with 3-channel capacity, you can fit several cables in this clever cord cover. Then when it’s time to make changes, the two top loading channel will make changes a breeze by simply pulling out the cord you don’t need. Also available in single channel cord cover called Compact Cord Protector.

"Simple Design, Big Solution"

For more information, please visit www.ut-wire.com/cp
